*   ## **_WILL OSPREAY DEF. BRYAN KEITH_**
    

Great match that ended with a Styles Clash into a hidden blade. Post match, Will Ospreay and Kyle Fletcher get into a brawl in the audience

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c31b37aa-0182-48eb-85a2-cb310b3cc50a/20250226_173636.jpg)

