![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/294f766e-c097-4587-9053-825499555eda/20250226_175040.jpg)

*   ## **_THE OUTRUNNERS DEF THE MURDER MACHINES AFTER A DISTRACTION FROM THE HURT SYNDICATE_**
    

The Outrunners will get a shot at the Hurt Business and the AEW Tag Team Championships

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1ebab372-7f21-45b1-9d42-4ec35ef4291b/received_1146594083575171.jpeg)

Mercedes Moné is backstage cutting a promo on Momo Watanabe when she runs into Billie Starks and slaps a cup of water into her face like a nobody.

Starks gets in Mercedes face saying Mone knows exactly who she is. Starks is about to get physical with Mone when Momo Watanabe sneaks up from behind with her baseball bat. Billie tells Mercedes to watch her back, Mercedes sees Momo and runs away.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c3be5d4f-e61d-4fcb-b111-c06a2db97792/Screenshot_20250226_175809.jpg)

Swerve Strickland says he's been far too distracted with Ricochet. Swerve wants championship gold. But he has to right the wrong that is Ricochet wearing the crown jewel robe.

Ricochet interrupted Swerve to say that he doesn't want anything to do with him anymore. He also wants championship gold.

Prince Nana has an offer for Ricochet. Winner of Ricochet vs Swerve Strickland at AEW Revolution will be the number one contender for the AEW World Championship.

Ricochet leaves but Prince Nana stops Swerve from leaving. Nana says he needs Swerve to go back to who he was. Prince Nana has done too much for Swerve and taken too many bullets.

If Swerve doesn't get the robe back, Prince Nana can't be by his side anymore.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/44fb4dfb-4b52-4fa0-bccb-1ea119b17163/20250226_180723.jpg)

