*   ## **_UNDISPUTED def. Daniel Garcia and FTR_**
    

Adam Cole pinned Daniel Garcia earning him a shot at the TNT Championship this Saturday on Collision

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9154b7c0-bcd2-4044-9f4c-8d7133bfa16a/20250226_182416.jpg)

