![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2b109942-cdc5-4c05-931c-83eb650bee05/20250226_182617.jpg)

Adam Copeland tries to take on the Death Riders but they have the upper hand until Jay White appears to help.

Copeland pulls Shafir into one of Wheeler Yuta’s Flying Knees. He CON-CHAIR-TOs Claudio then lays Marina on a chair as well.

WILLOW NIGHTINGALE TAKES THE CHAIR FROM ADAM COPELAND HITS MARINA SHAIFR WITH A CONCHAIRTO, HERSELF!!!

Adam Copeland has now taken out PAC, Claudio and Marina Shafir with Conchairtos!

Mox and Yuta are all alone headed into Revolution

